{"tid":816634,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用家福音Apple不再提供3.5mm耳機轉插","createTime":"2018-09-13T01:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T01:17:50.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2344a73e838cf73ff72d018d7bef14a8fea4ce","tid":816634,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"隨著新 iPhone 的發表，自然也會有一批老款 iPhone 被撤下貨架。不過這次的情況有點特殊，因為被「淘汰」的 iPhone SE 和 6s 系列（其實 iPhone X 也沒了），已經是最後一批帶有 3.5mm 耳機插孔的 Apple 手機了。不光如此，在新出的 iPhone Xs、Xs Max 和 XR 上還有一個變化，那就是在這三款新機的出廠包裝中，已經不再含有能助你過渡到無線時代的 Lightning to 3.5mm 轉接線。當然囉，這樣配件你也可以單買，不過 Apple 肯定還是希望你去買他們的無線耳機，或至少是帶 Lightning 插頭的產品吧"},{"pid":"cc41ebd67d8b411444b97ef6b73f87f5349a1410","tid":816634,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕版，好似條線未壞"},{"pid":"70e9ade1118fed86a12265a1b51c7121f0bff9dd","tid":816634,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"我部SE仲順到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851382c5b36432b15398b9a4c1a153645aabc673","tid":816634,"uid":30510,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"70e9ade1118fed86a12265a1b51c7121f0bff9dd","tid":816634,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"我部SE仲順到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"我部3gs玩pubg日半都未用完啲電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0c37fa19a1049f40230f6fc3c94fe0a357beb7","tid":816634,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"無用3.5mm好耐"}]}